The project manager opens the meeting by recapping the discussions of the previous meeting , telling the group this meeting's agenda , and stating what each person will do for the next meeting.
Then the industrial designer talks about the components design and explains exactly what remotes do and how they operate.
He also talks about batteries and chips.
The interface specialist present research from the internet about user interface.
